name: Grey Superskewing of 512
description: Created with curiosity about the visual consequences of invented rules.  The Superskew loop of the natural numbers sequence image.   For each single-pixel row in turn, all rows below are shifted 1 pixel to the right and XORed with the previous result.  After all of them are skewed, they straighten back and the process is repeated. 64 animation copies differ by one time frame overlapped with 1/64 opacity, 512 gen., rotated 90CW, 1/4 frame rate, cropped to 2/3. GIF 1024x512px 128f Gdańsk 2021
